# Tick3t doctrine

Before implementing features, align with:

- [VISION.md](../../VISION.md) — product north star
- [ROADMAP.md](../../ROADMAP.md) — current phase is **Phase 1** unless the user says otherwise
- [ARCHITECTURE.md](../../ARCHITECTURE.md) — Tick3t vs RedFace Pay boundaries
- [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) — implementation rules

**Tick3t** = event operating system. **RedFace Pay** = money. Do not duplicate payments inside Tick3t. Ticket checkout lines use `ticket_type_id`, never catalog `product_id`.
